graph TD
  A[runner holds current CourtState] --> B{Lean request}
  B -->|initialize_case| C[seed complaint, attachments,\nand court profile]
  B -->|role_view| D[return role-scoped case view]
  B -->|next_opportunity| E[derive one current opportunity]
  B -->|apply_decision| F[validate pass or legal act]
  B -->|step| G[apply resulting action state]

  E --> H[agent sees current role view<br/>and one constrained opportunity]
  H --> I[agent submits pass or decision]
  I --> F
  F --> J{valid?}
  J -->|no| K[error with actor_message\nno state change]
  J -->|yes| L[accepted action or recorded pass]
  L --> N[runner executes accepted act\nor records pass]
  N --> G
  G --> M[updated authoritative state]
  C --> M
  D --> H
  K --> H
  M --> E
